Package io.github.nixtabyte.telegram.jtelebot.server.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractCommand
    Abstract implementation of Command in order to contain a Message and RequestHandler for further manipulation of the Bot.
    AbstractCommandDispatcher
    Abstract implementation of CommandDispatcher, Observer, Service and Runnable which uses a runnable thread with a service pattern behavior (start|stop) in order to enqueue Command objects and then execute them one by one.
    AbstractCommandTask
    Abstract component that extends Observable and implements CommandTask and Runnable in order to handle the execution of every individual Command into a separated runnable thread.
    AbstractCommandWatcher
    Abstract polling implementation of CommandWatcher, Service and Runnable which uses a runnable thread with a service pattern behavior (start|stop) in order to retrieve commands periodically from the Telegram service (Those commands are supposed to be originated by a User).
    DefaultCommandDispatcher
    Main implementation of CommandDispatcher that extends the AbstractCommandDispatcher behavior in order to handle a sort of DefaultCommandTask instances as part of a ThreadPoolExecutor.
    DefaultCommandQueue  
    DefaultCommandTask  
    DefaultCommandWatcher
    Main implementation of CommandWatcher that extends the AbstractCommandWatcher behavior in order to implement a polling component service for the Telegram Bot API service.
